Package: Firehoods
Title: Neighbouhood Index for  Wildfire Likelihood Estimation
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R:
	person("Douglas", "Radford", , "douglas.radford@adelaide.edu.au", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-2237-4807"))
Description: This package provides a function (neighbouhood.function) 
    to estimate wildfire likelihood using the methods of Radford et al. 2024. 
	Details of this implementation can be found in the publication listed below.
	When using the package, we ask that the below publication is cited.
	publication: Radford, DAG, Maier, HRM, van Delden, H, Zecchin, AZ, Jeanneau, A 2024. An efficient, multi-scale neighbourhood index to quantify wildfire likelihood. The International Journal of Wildland Fire. DOI: 10.1071/WF23055
Encoding: UTF-8
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
